data.description: *Price Adjustment!* Welcome to your dream home on the luxurious Island in Daybreak! The main floor welcomes you with a large living room, while the second floor boasts an open kitchen, dining area, and family room with many windows and natural light. Step outside to a charming balcony, perfect for enjoying the picturesque surroundings of The Island. The third floor is a private oasis, featuring the main bedroom with an en-suite bathroom and two additional bedrooms. This home boasts a large driveway that you can actually park 2 vehicles in, a rare thing for Daybreak! One of very few townhomes on The Island, come take advantage of the vibrant community and the amenities it offers, from private parks, fire pits and walking trails, to nearby shops and restaurants. Sale includes TAX ID 27-18-357-017.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records.  The buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
